. We have argued strongly in f</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">avour of Part P, and were supportive of the Committee’s recommendation that it should be retained.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">1.5</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">We believe that the Competent Persons Scheme remains the best and most cost</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">-</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">effective </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">way to maintain standards amongst electrical contractors</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">1.6</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">However, we</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> have seriously</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> considered</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> the written evidence of individual contractors who expressed concern</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">s over the existing system</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> and have sought </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">in this response </span><span style="font-family:'Minion 